### Create a new student
POST http://localhost:3000/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Alice Smith",
    "grade": "B",
    "email": "alice.smith@example.com"
}

### Retrieve all students
GET http://localhost:3000/students

### Retrieve a student by ID (replace {id} with the actual ID, e.g., 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/students/1

### Update a student by ID (replace {id} with the actual ID, e.g., 1)
PUT http://localhost:3000/students/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Alice Johnson",
    "grade": "A",
    "email": "alice.johnson@newmail.com"
}

### Delete a student by ID (replace {id} with the actual ID, e.g., 1)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/students/1
